content: Yes, that's right! Seattle is renowned for its coffee culture, and is home to some of the most famous coffee chains in the world such as Starbucks and Tully's Coffee. Some of the other popular coffee shops in Seattle include Victrola Coffee Roasters, Cafe Mox, Caffe Umbria, Monorail Espresso, and Seattle Coffee Works among others. If you are a fan of coffee, Seattle is definitely a city you would love to visit!
